meta {
  name: Subscribe New Transaction
  type: ws
  seq: 2
}

ws {
  url: wss://bitcoin-mainnet.g.alchemy.com/v2/{{api_key}}
  body: ws
  auth: inherit
}

body:ws {
  name: subscribe
  type: json
  content: '''
    {
      "id": "2",
      "method": "subscribeNewTransaction",
      "params": {}
    }
  '''
}

docs {
  Emits every new transaction added to the blockchain, across all addresses.

  On subscribe, returns a confirmation that the subscription is active. Subsequent events include normalized transaction details.

  This is a high-volume firehose subscription and may not be enabled on all networks. If you do not receive events after subscribing, use subscribeAddresses for targeted updates instead.

  https://www.alchemy.com/docs/bitcoin/utxo-websockets#subscribenewtransaction
}
